-- Citigroup Hires Valentin Marinov, Greg Anderson for Currency Strategy Team
-- B y   P a u l   D o b s o n
-- 2010-10-07T15:32:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-07/citigroup-hires-marinov-anderson-for-foreign-exchange-strategy.html
Citigroup Inc. said it hired  Valentin Marinov  and  Greg Anderson  to work on its foreign-exchange
strategy team.  Marinov was hired as a currency strategist in London,
having held similar roles at Societe Generale SA and Dresdner
Bank, Citigroup said today in an e-mailed statement.  Anderson will work as a senior currency strategist in New
York, also joining from Societe Generale, Citigroup said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Paul Dobson in London at 
 pdobson2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Daniel Tilles at 
 dtilles@bloomberg.net  